&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen at this Practice and we are looking for a GP with a professional,enthusiastic and flexible approach to join our team. We are looking for a salaried GP, who is either experiencedor recently qualified,who is considering the next step into partnership. We currently have two partners, onefull time and onepart time. Hours and sessions are negotiable but we would require a minimum of4 sessions per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our practice is well established within the Waldersladearea with 6000 patients and is part of the newly formed Medway South PCN. We are a friendly and flexible team who achieved a rating of GOOD in the 2016 CQC inspection and is aconsistently high achiever on QoF and other services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please feel free to contact the Practice Manager if you would like to meet the Partners to discuss this position and view the premises.&lt;/p&gt;
